Citing siteinterlock


If you use siteinterlock as part of your workflow in a scientific publication, please cite siteinterlock as:


@misc{raschkas ...,
  author       = {Raschka, Sebastian, ...},
  title        = {siteinterlock paper},
  month        = sep,
  year         = 2016,
  doi          = {...},
  url          = {...}
}
